Winston and Weston Doty https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Winston_and_Weston_Doty 0 Winston and Weston Doty (February 18, 1914 – January 1, 1934) were twin child actors active for several years during the silent film era. The Doty twins were among the casualties of the New Year Flood of 1934.
